race.comment: ACCREDITED (8) is progressing well scoring last time out (29.27) at Sandown and bringing up his 8th career win. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Looks to have an edge on most of these. WEBLEC BILLY (6) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and two minors from eight tries. Below best last time at this track (30.99) in a Special conditions G3, finishing a 16 length fifth. Looks well placed here and among the chances. SWEET SUNDOWN (1) was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a second place finish (29.56) at Sandown two back. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won four of eight tries. The form out of last race has been strong. Expected to run well. KING OWEN (4) picked up a cheque over this course and distance most recently - in the mix again.
